<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>SCP-CN-1945</strong></p>
<p><strong>著作資訊</strong><br />
<strong>作者：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/reverberate-a" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255954); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569465" alt="Reverberate_a" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/reverberate-a" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255954); return false;">Reverberate_a</a></span><br />
